content:
Enable the Account Owner Report

The Account Owner report lists all accounts and who owns them.

Available in: Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.
Customize Application permission is needed to show or hide account owner report.

Organizations with private account sharing model can restrict users from running the Account Owner report. 

To show or hide this report:

From Setup, enter Account Owner Report, then select Account Owner Report.
Select the checkbox to allow all users to run this report.
Click Save.
title: Enable Account Owner Report in Salesforce
